snippet.title: Bunny Beats Gameplay Showcase (2020)
snippet.description:
Bunny Beats is a rhythm learning game that challenges you to use your ears to master an endless variety of procedurally generated rhythms! Get to know the gameplay and special features in Bunny Beats with this gameplay showcase video, first seen at Anime Central 2020 Online!

Please wishlist Bunny Beats on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/917640/Bunny_Beats/
Follow Studio Tapioca on Twitter for the latest updates: https://twitter.com/StudioTapioca

We are looking for players for device testing! Please send us a DM on Twitter if interested :)

#rhythmgame #indiegame #indiedev #steam #videogame #bunny
